<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243650>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Coleophora serinipennella. A, B, male (CBNUPM000025, 000026); C, D, female (CBNUPM000028, 000027); E, outer view of labial palpus; F, inner view of labial palpus; G, outer view of hindleg; H, inner view of hindleg; I, male venation, wings slide no. KJM0338; J, close-up of frenulum; K, female venation, wings slide no. KJM0339; L, close-up of frenulum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8243650/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243654>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Genitalia and abdomen of Coleophora serinipennella. A, male genitalia, gen. slide no. KJM0277; B, phallus; C, part of male genitalia, gen. slide no. KJM0276; D, male abdomen (terga left, sterna right, gen. slide no. KJM0277); E, female genitalia, gen. slide no. KJM0278; F, close-up of sterigma+colliculum; G, close-up of signum, H, close-up of ostium bursae+posterior part of colliculum, gen. slide no. KJM0265; I, close-up of signum; J, female abdomen (terga left, sterna right, gen. slide no. KJM0278)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8243654/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

